descript.abstract: This is a detailed polygon shape file of the official citywide recognized neighborhood boundaries.
descript.purpose: To show the officially recognized neighborhood boundaries within the City of Sacramento.
descript.supplinf: Note: These neighborhood boundaries are not the same as the neighborhood association boundaries. These boundaries indicate neighborhoods based on geographic and social characteristics. Neighborhood boundaries for this purpose do not overlap.
